{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, one of the most disturbing-- most disturbing things for me while I was working there is to listen to the conversation of my coworkers, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] especially right after the ghetto-- the burning of the ghetto, how they were very pleased that, finally, they did the Jews in.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to just stand there and listen to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have-- I couldn't go to the extent of chiming in to hope that they would not consider me different from them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I couldn't bring myself to go in that far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As far as the Germans, we had nothing to do with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans treated Poles as second-class citizens to begin with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they wouldn't-- Germans would not lower themselves to discussing anything with the Polish employees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Polish employees, however, did discuss the issues among themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it wasn't pretty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't pretty at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no talk about camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew such a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody, at that time, knew about camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What we did know, after the Warsaw Ghetto, we did know that they took them away to the east.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not hear the word 'Treblinka.' Although the transports from the Warsaw Ghetto went to Treblinka, I do not recall hearing the word 'Treblinka' until liberation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not hear the word 'Auschwitz' until liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that there were those horrible camps, labor camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, as I said, we knew that nobody returned from those labor camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I did not have any idea that there were gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Understand, we did not-- after we left Warsaw, we did not have any access to the underground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not know what was coming through the shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
